            </div>
            <div class="ousStory_div3">
                <div class="l shave_img"><img src="images/shave_05.jpg" width="100%"></div>
                <div class="r shave_div">
                    <h2>One For Old</h2>
                    <p>Because of population structure imbalance problem of China in short future, we will invest more resources into the construction of nursing home care . </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
